    "The model includes firm age, age squared, customer status, and regional indicators. Age squared is included because the relationship between firm age and patent production may not be perfectly linear.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Coding the Poisson Regression Log-Likelihood"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "id": "f0c7024c",
   "metadata": {},
